query: SELECT YEAR(e.evaluationDate) as yr, MONTH(e.evaluationDate) as mo, t.teamName, t.id as teamId, COUNT(*) as cnt, MIN(e.evaluationDate) as minDate, MAX(e.evaluationDate) as maxDate FROM evaluations e LEFT JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.gamePresenterId = gp.id LEFT JOIN fm_teams t ON gp.teamId = t.id GROUP BY yr, mo, t.id, t.teamName;
